        "# 6. Experiment 2: Automatic Opacity Estimation\n",
        "\n",
        "Automatic opacity is computed as:\n",
        "\n",
        "    opacity = 1 - cosine_similarity(expression, components)\n",
        "\n",
        "Lower similarity indicates higher semantic opacity."
      ],
